This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the learnability of models via neural network algorithms. It could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it specifically focuses on the use of neural networks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as neural networks are a popular tool in AI research. The paper also deals with the efficiency of learning, which could place it under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
